This tool will create a "workspace" directory under your script directory, and all the logs, images, etc. will reside there.

How to use this tool:
1. install pyudev (optional): 
   $cd pyudev-0.11/
   $sudo python setup.py install

2. run the downloader:
   $python downloader.py

3. run the burner:
   $python burner.py

